@startuml
title AI Rephrase Tool - Sequence Diagram

actor User

participant "Streamlit UI" as Streamlit
participant "AWS API Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "AWS Lambda" as Lambda
participant "Groq API\n(Llama 3.3)" as Groq

User -> Streamlit : Enter text\nSelect tone & language\nSelect variants\nClick Rephrase Button

Streamlit -> APIGateway : POST /rephrase\nJSON Payload

activate APIGateway

APIGateway -> Lambda : Invoke Lambda Function

activate Lambda

Lambda -> Lambda : Build Prompt

Lambda -> Groq : HTTPS Chat Completion Request

activate Groq

Groq --> Lambda : AI Generated Paraphrases

deactivate Groq

Lambda -> Lambda : Parse & Format Response

Lambda --> APIGateway : JSON Response

deactivate Lambda

APIGateway --> Streamlit : HTTP 200 Response

deactivate APIGateway

Streamlit --> User : Display Paraphrased Variants

@enduml